query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS plan_enrollments (
  id VARCHAR(36) PRIMARY KEY,
  plan_id VARCHAR(36) NOT NULL,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  enrolled_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  expires_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  last_accessed_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  status ENUM('Ativo', 'Expirado', 'Cancelado', 'Suspenso') DEFAULT 'Ativo' NOT NULL,
  daily_hours INT DEFAULT 4 NOT NULL,
  custom_settings JSON DEFAULT ('{}'),
  created_by INT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  UNIQUE INDEX idx_unique_enrollment (plan_id, user_id),
  INDEX idx_user_plans (user_id, status),
  INDEX idx_plan_enrollments (plan_id, status),
  INDEX idx_expired_enrollments (expires_at),
  FOREIGN KEY (plan_id) REFERENCES plans(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
)
